data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.25% VA Loan!!! Beautifully custom, freshly painted 4 bedroom/2 bathroom on a cul de sac within 5 minutes of Fort Liberty main gate. Charming home with gorgeous updated kitchen and bathrooms!  Large family room with a vaulted ceiling and tiled floor that is opened to the kitchen/dining room. Remodeled kitchen with upgraded soft close cabinets, granite counters, pantry, tile floor and backsplash. Matching Frigidaire appliances. Guest full bathroom has Tuscan inspired full walk in shower with beautiful tile work. Bedrooms have fully carpet. Wooden deck overlooks spacious fenced  in backyard with bricked fire pit area.  Huge wired storage shed to use as a workshop or "she-shed" with drywall interior! New Roof and HVAC in 2017. Ring Camera system stays with the alarm system. Easy commute and access to shopping, work, interstate. Perfect starter home. Don't let this one get away!
